<item>
            <title>[LU-8005] LBUG on osc_req_attr_set</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8005</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After new readahead code is introduced, client could die with the following backtrace.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
